00:00:16.309 --> 00:00:22.300
Oh, because he didn't.

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:27.440
Well, what did Jesus teach his disciples to pray?

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:33.899
Oh, yeah, well, I know the obvious.

00:00:33.899 --> 00:00:38.899
Let your kingdom come, implied future tents.

00:00:38.899 --> 00:00:41.899
