00:00:56.399 --> 00:00:59.399
Maybe you were to study ahead of time.

00:00:59.399 --> 00:01:01.399
How about no?

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:02.399
I'm really swamped.

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:04.400
I know you're busy.

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:05.400
