00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:21.500
I thought she was making our study a priority,

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:23.500
but maybe she wasn't.

00:01:23.500 --> 00:01:59.019
Next week, it's dual die time.

00:01:59.019 --> 00:02:03.019
Then, I remembered 1 Corinthians 3 verse 6

00:02:03.019 --> 00:02:06.019
that God keeps making it grow.

00:02:06.019 --> 00:02:19.069
So I asked him to help Jade.

00:02:19.069 --> 00:02:21.069
Then left it with him.

00:02:21.069 --> 00:02:47.139
Look, I need to apologize.

00:02:47.139 --> 00:02:49.139
Forget it.

00:02:49.139 --> 00:02:51.139
You were stressed.

00:02:51.139 --> 00:02:53.139
Yeah, but there's more.

00:02:53.139 --> 00:02:55.139
Inside, I knew you were right.

00:02:55.139 --> 00:02:58.139
It's just the last thing I wanted to stop.

00:02:59.139 --> 00:03:00.139
Really?

00:03:00.139 --> 00:03:17.240
How about I show you how I prepare?

00:03:17.240 --> 00:03:18.240
Okay.
